                            <li><p>Merging</p></li><li><p> Searching</p></li><li><p>Partitioning</p></li><li><p> Swapping only</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Partitioning</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
