                    </div>

                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Order from Within</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>Which traversal of a Binary Search Tree (BST) produces the elements in non-decreasing sorted order?</p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Preorder</p></li><li><p>Postorder</p></li><li><p>Level Order</p></li><li><p>Inorder</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Inorder</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
                <div class="question-container">
