                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tallest Shape Scenario</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>What is the maximum height of a binary tree with N nodes?</p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>N/2</p></li><li><p>N − 1</p></li><li><p>log₂(N)</p></li><li><p>2N</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>N − 1</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
                <div class="question-container">
