                    </div>

                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Recursive Accumulation Insight</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>What does this function return for a binary tree root?</p><pre><code>int solve(Node* r) {
  if(!r) return 0;
  return 1 + solve(r-&gt;left) + solve(r-&gt;right);
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Number of leaf nodes</p></li><li><p>The sum of all node values</p></li><li><p>The height of the tree</p></li><li><p>Total number of nodes</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Total number of nodes</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
                <div class="question-container">
                    <div class="header-badges">
                        <span>Q44</span>
                        <span class="complexity-Medium">Medium</span>
                        <span style="background-color: #eff6ff; color: #1d4ed8;">MCQ</span>
                    </div>

                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Terminal Node Tracker</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>What is the behavior of this recursive snippet?</p><pre><code>int mystery(Node* r) {
  if(!r) return 0;
  if(!r-&gt;left &amp;&amp; !r-&gt;right) return 1;
  return mystery(r-&gt;left) + mystery(r-&gt;right);
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Counts total nodes</p></li><li><p>Finds the max depth</p></li><li><p>Counts leaf nodes</p></li><li><p>Counts internal nodes</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Counts leaf nodes</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
