                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Radix Sort Dependency</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>Radix sort relies fundamentally on which other sorting principle or algorithm component to sort elements at each digit/position efficiently?</p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>A comparison-based sort </p></li><li><p>A stable linear time sort</p></li><li><p>Recursion and partitioning</p></li><li><p>The Sieve of Eratosthenes principle</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>A stable linear time sort</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
                <div class="question-container">
