    int maxVal = *max_element(arr, arr+n);
    for(int exp = 1; maxVal/exp &gt; 0; exp *= 10)
        countingSortByDigit(arr, n, exp);
}</code></pre><p>If the maximum value in the array is <strong>999</strong>, how many passes does radix sort make?</p>
