                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Hashing</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>Analyze this C++ code. What is the value of <strong>table[3] </strong>after execution?</p><pre><code>int m = 5, table[5] = {-1, -1, -1, -1, -1};
for(int k : {3, 8, 13}) {
    int i = 0;
    while(table[(k%m + i)%m] != -1) i++;
    table[(k%m + i)%m] = k;
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>-1</p></li><li><p>8</p></li><li><p>3</p></li><li><p>13</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>3</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
