                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tree traversal</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>What happens in this specific traversal variant?</p><pre><code>void t(Node* r) {
  if(!r || !r-&gt;left) return;
  swap(r-&gt;data, r-&gt;left-&gt;data);
  t(r-&gt;left);
  t(r-&gt;right);
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Propagates root value down the left spine</p></li><li><p>Standard Pre-order</p></li><li><p>Infinite loop</p></li><li><p>Mirrors the tree</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Propagates root value down the left spine</p></div>

                    <hr style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;" />
                </div>
            
                <div class="question-container">
