                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tree traversal</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>Which traversal pattern is being modified here?</p><pre><code>void visit(Node* r) {
  if(!r) return;
  if(r-&gt;data % 2 == 0) visit(r-&gt;left);
  cout &lt;&lt; r-&gt;data &lt;&lt; " ";
  if(r-&gt;data % 2 != 0) visit(r-&gt;right);
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Standard In-order</p></li><li><p>Conditional In-order</p></li><li><p>Pre-order Search</p></li><li><p>Binary Search Tree Search</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Conditional In-order</p></div>

