                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>What is the output for a tree where Root is 10, Left is 4, and Right is 6?</p><pre><code>int calc(Node* r) {
  if(!r) return 0;
  int s = calc(r-&gt;left) + calc(r-&gt;right);
  if(s == 0) return r-&gt;data;
  cout &lt;&lt; r-&gt;data &lt;&lt; " ";
  return s + r-&gt;data;
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
