                    <h2 style="font-size: 16pt; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tree traversal</h2>

                    <div style="font-size: 12pt;">
                        <p>Which traversal is represented here?</p><pre><code>stack&lt;Node*&gt; s; 
s.push(root);
while(!s.empty()) {
  Node* c = s.top(); s.pop();
  cout &lt;&lt; c-&gt;data &lt;&lt; " ";
  if(c-&gt;right) s.push(c-&gt;right);
  if(c-&gt;left) s.push(c-&gt;left);
}</code></pre><p></p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <h3>Options:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p>Level-order</p></li><li><p>Post-order</p></li><li><p>Pre-order</p></li><li><p>In-order</p></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><div style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d;">Correct Answer: <p>Pre-order</p></div>

